{"tid":56748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國被批支持「沖繩獨立」　圖分裂日本輿論","createTime":"2016-12-27T13:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:46:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f68556dfec6905126494cc2ea4ace6e29a1baf4","tid":56748,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"世界輪流轉，中國企圖分裂日本！日本情報機關之一的公安調查廳，上周發表報告指，有中國的大學和智庫在背後支持沖繩要求獨立的組織，並與他們建聯繫，試圖分裂日本國內的公眾輿論。<br />\n<br />\n日本公安調查廳的報告顯示，中國與這些獨立組織加強聯繫的動機是在日本國內製造分歧，將公眾輿論導向對中國有利的方向。報告還警告日本必須關注中國方面在沖繩的活動。但中國外交部尚未對這一指控，作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n公安調查廳提到，8月12日中國官媒《環球時報》刊出一篇評論，認為中國應該用古名「琉球」稱呼沖繩，因為使用「沖繩」的稱呼就等於承認日本的主權。<br />\n<br />\n駐日美軍有7成集中在沖繩。近年沖繩與日本中央政府的關係轉趨緊張，沖繩140萬居民之中，有許多人對美軍駐紮當地感到反感。本月22日，沖繩縣知事翁長雄志缺席美軍歸還「北部訓練場」土地的儀式，改為參加抗議美軍魚鷹運輸機迫降事故的集會，縣議會更在翁長雄志主導下通過決議，對美軍提出抗議。當天中央政府通過的明年度預算，削減沖繩經費百分之六，被解讀為有意教訓不聽話的翁長雄志。<br />\n<br />\n不過，沖繩獨立運動並不具人氣。去年5月沖繩「琉球新報」的民調顯示，三分之二民眾偏好維持現狀，兩成一希望沖繩有更多自治權，僅百分之八想要獨立。"},{"pid":"b5f2ab4c67890690ef06422e15c357c06a5d00d9","tid":56748,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161227&amp;guid=56097743&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161227%26guid%3D56097743%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=CWRTqE1GfqspQNwmIOWEoBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=b4191f22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161227%26guid%3D56097743%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=4159fea6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161227&amp;guid=56097743&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9ab98fa38777735ed2105953db003d3ca9a918f3","tid":56748,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cdc844357c9471224b77dcedd3130b9f851cbf","tid":56748,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"唔好咁雙重標準呀<br />\n香港都要獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce0478217c88131ab8ae1b0f7d72c7cb5850fa4","tid":56748,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZwbUnr8PwVZz7JLjkGu7Ze5M3NfSsByKASVGzZ3NSrh3?filename=v0Y2A7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0Y2A7X.jpg&h=2c551ab2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24a254d99c92ef768defbe96c8d80a75c5b084da","tid":56748,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02a3bf71e878e741bbfb6a15b9b0afabeb00e93","tid":56748,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b8c88cb6fe3f7bd3623a9cb195f7622c667377c","tid":56748,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"其實沖繩 可以一方面獨立, 獨立完之後繼續親美"}]}